  <brief_title>Lifestyle Intervention in Patients With New Onset Type 2 Diabetes.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Intensive Lifestyle Intervention on Hormonal Factors Regulating Food Intake and Blood Glucose Control in Patients With New Onset Type 2 Diabetes.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
