  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study seeks to establish if weight loss achieved through a program of intensive lifestyle
      management can result in improvements in GLP-1 and glycaemic control, in patients with newly
      diagnosed type 2 diabetes mellitus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
